CONTRIBUTING.md
     1вҶ’# Contributing
     3вҶ’1. [Fork it](https://help.github.com/articles/fork-a-repo/)
     4вҶ’2. Install dependencies (`npm install`)
     5вҶ’3. Create your feature branch (`git checkout -b my-new-feature`)
     6вҶ’4. Commit your changes (`git commit -am 'Added some feature'`)
     7вҶ’5. Test your changes (`npm test`)
     8вҶ’6. Push to the branch (`git push origin my-new-feature`)
     9вҶ’7. [Create new Pull Request](https://help.github.com/articles/creating-a-pull-request/)
    10вҶ’
    11вҶ’## Testing
    13вҶ’We use [TAP](https://github.com/tapjs/node-tap) to write tests. Run our test suite with this command:
    14вҶ’
    15вҶ’```
    16вҶ’npm test
    17вҶ’```
    18вҶ’
    19вҶ’## Code Style
    21вҶ’We use [standard](https://www.npmjs.com/package/standard) and [editorconfig](http://editorconfig.org) to maintain code style and best practices. Please make sure your PR adheres to the guides by running:
    22вҶ’
    23вҶ’```
    24вҶ’npm run lint
    25вҶ’```
